text: Ormenoides is a genus of flatid planthoppers in the family Flatidae. ==Species== These 6 species belong to the genus Ormenoides: * Ormenoides distincta * Ormenoides laevis * Ormenoides pauperata * Ormenoides pehlkei * Ormenoides subflava * Ormenoides venusta Ormenoides venusta ==References== Category:Flatidae Category:Auchenorrhyncha genera
title: Ormenoides
